text:
Name: Marie Friedman.
Graduation Year: 2023.
Description: Marie Friedman is a dedicated Mechanical Engineering student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in mechanical engineering research and practical applications. They aspire to become a doctor specializing in cardiology and patient care. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
